{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VKwUjerhpXXmPiZBXxgbiy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The driveId or itemId might be incorrect, or the Graph API doesn't have access. Let me try fetching the item metadata first (without /content) to see if the drive exists.\n\nActually, the Loop page is in a content storage container. Let me try to first verify the drive exists, then list items.\n\nWait, let me reconsider. The URL structure is:\n`/contentstorage/x8FNO-xtskuCRX2_fMTHLRo8YaOBF1tMsxtMIJmILxo`\n\nThis is a content storage container, which maps to a specific site/drive in SharePoint. \n\nI should try accessing it through the sites API instead. The `s` parameter decoded to that content storage path, which gives me the site URL: `microsoft.sharepoint-df.com/contentstorage/x8FNO-xtskuCRX2_fMTHLRo8YaOBF1tMsxtMIJmILxo`. Let me construct a proper Graph request using this.\n\nActually, I think the issue might be with the base64 encoding of the `driveId` - it's URL-safe base64, not standard. Let me try resolving the site first through the Graph API, then accessing the drive from there.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":523,"cache_read_input_tokens":46727,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":523,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4004397f-9402-4049-ba0c-52ed9b7104fc","uuid":"4adfa1f8-c8c3-4767-afb7-dc27bff39355"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VKwUjerhpXXmPiZBXxgbiy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Hpb7yyDLsmQmgPYSNTRtQD","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst https = require('https');\nconst { execSync } = require('child_process');\nconst token = execSync('az account get-access-token --resource https://graph.microsoft.com --query accessToken -o tsv', {encoding:'utf8'}).trim();\n\n// Try to get the site by server-relative URL first\nconst sitePath = '/v1.0/sites/microsoft.sharepoint-df.com:/contentstorage/x8FNO-xtskuCRX2_fMTHLRo8YaOBF1tMsxtMIJmILxo';\nconst opts = {\n  hostname: 'graph.microsoft.com',\n  path: encodeURI(sitePath),\n  headers: { 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token }\n};\nhttps.get(opts, (res) => {\n  let data = '';\n  res.on('data', c => data += c);\n  res.on('end', () => {\n    console.log('Status:', res.statusCode);\n    console.log(data.substring(0, 3000));\n  });\n});\n\" 2>&1","description":"Resolve SharePoint site from content storage path","timeout":30000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":523,"cache_read_input_tokens":46727,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":523,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4004397f-9402-4049-ba0c-52ed9b7104fc","uuid":"f3e6eacc-b063-4959-990c-e8c295c4417b"}
