{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01DFvPTr3iVfkG9uJXzbMqAt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still 404. The issue might be with the driveId encoding. Let me check if there's a URL-encoding issue. The driveId `b!lRZQfeTZQ0C9IoRwG5pqAiArSWyR8NpBioqVzLj3MH9F-3RQf0crQokI7f1IpihS` is the one from the nav parameter. But Loop might expect the driveId differently.\n\nWait — I just realized something. The nav parameter `d` value was URL-encoded as `b%21lRZQfeTZQ0C9IoRwG5pqAiArSWyR8NpBioqVzLj3MH9F-3RQf0crQokI7f1IpihS`. \n\nWhen I decode that, I get `b!lRZQfeTZQ0C9IoRwG5pqAiArSWyR8NpBioqVzLj3MH9F-3RQf0crQokI7f1IpihS`. But I'm noticing a discrepancy — the driveId contains `MH9F` while the workspace decoded value shows `MG9F`. Let me trace through the workspace string more carefully to see where the mismatch is.\n\nLooking at the full decoded workspace, I see `ODSP|microsoft.sharepoint-df.com|b!lRZQfeTZQ0C9IoRwG5pqAiArSWyR8NpBioqVzLj3MG9F-3RQf0crQokI7f1IpihS|01KXJWT57EKQLXXWD3SZC2D422WJC7CMVD` — that's definitely `MG9F` in the driveId, but the `d` parameter shows `MH9F`. They differ by just one character, which could mean the workspace container and the page's drive are actually different resources.\n\nI'm wondering if this whole approach is off-base though. This is a \"contentstorage\" URL, which might use a different API pattern than what the Loop API expects. The Loop API could be restricted to only accessing pages from the user's Copilot workspace, not arbitrary content storage containers.\n\nLet me try a different angle — maybe I should test the sdf endpoint, list pages in this workspace first, or use the Graph API's sites endpoint with the beta version. Actually, the most direct approach might be to just call the SharePoint API with curl and a SharePoint token instead.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1335,"cache_read_input_tokens":48154,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1335,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4004397f-9402-4049-ba0c-52ed9b7104fc","uuid":"01efe869-dc90-426b-9951-558f7908f408"}
